ces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5bd21c7f75901d5115e962084f00487e201931","tid":174702,"uid":60065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T04:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有時搭巴士一上車聞到浸味已經想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 一多站就會好辛苦<br />\n但而家學緊車, 每次揸1.5hr都唔會暈"},{"pid":"17da40baec6083f0c5a00b48040d61ccbe786691","tid":174702,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:02:57.000Z","msg":"一開始暈就狂食芒果乾、話梅肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a70ff0fc8288961edd2d28494933fb959a3853b","tid":174702,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"我自己係唔聽歌好易暈，聽歌+望出窗就坐好耐都得"},{"pid":"e19daaf88332a53a0a883adf543ae41cfe8a247c","tid":174702,"uid":78572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:19:40.000Z","msg":"以前一定要聽歌 盡量要訓得著<br />\n訓唔到都要合埋眼 唔可以望景望電話<br />\n而家好少少可以望下電話但冇歌聽都一定會暈<br />\n仲有就係唔可以同朋友傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc3a49141925682573c608ec48ec509e7b04640","tid":174702,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"我以前都唔會<br />\n最近唔知做乜一禁電話 <br />\n五分鐘都暈<br />\n以前禁足成個鐘都無事"},{"pid":"be018f8297cd861be485d71d35e4f61bcc92d643","tid":174702,"uid":77314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前一直都暈車浪<br />\n暈到中六都係暈<br />\n直到入左u要搭車來回之後用一個月都唔夠就醫好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockqu